title: The 2019 Fantasy Superlatives | The Dantasy Football Podcast
description:
To close out the 2019 fantasy football season, we give out some season superlatives, including the Most Valuable Pick, Comeback Player of the Year, Waiver Wire League Winner, and the infamous Cool Uncle award.
Hosts: Danny Heifetz, Danny Kelly, and Craig Horlbeck
